{"id":38614,"date":"2023-01-16T14:37:07","date_gmt":"2023-01-16T10:37:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=38614"},"modified":"2023-01-16T14:37:07","modified_gmt":"2023-01-16T10:37:07","slug":"standing-firm","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/01\/16\/standing-firm\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Fitnah: Standing firm during end-times tribulations"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Soon there will come a time in which the people are sifted and only the dregs of humanity remain, their covenants and trusts are disordered, and they are set against each other.<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cHow should we be, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Keep to what you recognize as good and leave off what you recognize as evil. Turn your attention to your own personal affairs and leave off the affairs of the masses.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4342<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0635\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0648\u0634\u0650\u0643\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0623\u0652\u062a\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0632\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064c \u064a\u064f\u063a\u064e\u0